
Terminal comands: 
1. To chose the browser: --browser=chromium(firefox or webkit)
2. To see en real-time the test: --headed
3. To run all the tests: pytest. To run only one test: pytest folderName/fileName
4. To screenshots of final step: --screensot=on. Will be stored in pytest cache
5. To record video: --video=on 
6. To save html report of results: --html=report1.html (report1 can be any name)